No. 490,

Misc.

Bryant v. Wilkins, Warden. Petitioner pro se. Louis J. Lefkowitz, Attorney General of New York, and Anthony J. Lokot, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent.

Ct. App. N. Y. Certiorari denied on representation of Attorney General of New York that there is an adequate state remedy available to petitioner.
